{
  "url": "/cat/drinkware",
  "type": "root",
  "h1": "Custom Drinkware for Every Occasion",
  "metaTitle": "Custom Drinkware | Perfect Imprints",
  "metaDescription": "Shop custom drinkware for corporate events, trade shows, and employee gifts. Mugs, tumblers, coolers & more with your logo. Fast turnaround & low MOQ.",
  "introHtml": "<p>Whether you're stocking an employee breakroom, packing conference swag bags, or handing out refreshments at a charity 5K, custom drinkware puts your brand directly into people's hands. From stainless steel tumblers that keep coffee hot during morning meetings to insulated can coolers that keep sodas cold at company picnics, drinkware is a daily-use item recipients actually reach for.</p><p>Our drinkware category includes a wide range of styles, materials, and price points. Choose from double-wall vacuum tumblers like the 26 oz Tumbler, durable plastic cups like the 16 oz Uno Cup, or fun options like the Party Cup Set for tailgates. For outdoor workers or safety teams, the Basecamp® Icey provides rugged insulation. Coasters like the Slate Coaster and Stone Coaster make great add-ons or desk accessories.</p><p>Most items can be personalized with screen print, full-color digital print, or laser engraving. Minimums start as low as 50 pieces for many styles, and production typically ships within 7–10 business days. Perfect Imprints handles everything from artwork setup to bulk order fulfillment, so your branded drinkware arrives on time and on budget.</p>",
  "faqs": [
    {
      "q": "What is the minimum order quantity for custom drinkware?",
      "a": "Minimum order quantities vary by product. Many items like the 16 oz Uno Cup and Best Coolie start at 50 pieces. Tumblers and mugs often require 100–250 pieces. Contact our team for specific MOQs on your chosen item."
    },
    {
      "q": "What decoration methods are available for drinkware?",
      "a": "We offer screen printing, full-color digital printing, and laser engraving. Screen printing works well for simple logos on cylindrical surfaces. Digital printing allows detailed artwork. Laser engraving is best for stainless steel and gives a permanent, premium look."
    },
    {
      "q": "How long does production take for custom drinkware?",
      "a": "Standard production lead time is 7–10 business days after artwork approval. Rush orders may be available for an additional fee. Shipping time depends on your location and chosen carrier."
    },
    {
      "q": "Can I order a sample before placing a bulk order?",
      "a": "Yes, we can provide a blank sample of most drinkware items for a nominal fee, which is often credited toward your bulk order. Contact your sales representative to request a sample."
    },
    {
      "q": "Are custom drinkware items dishwasher and microwave safe?",
      "a": "It depends on the product. Stainless steel tumblers like the 26 oz Tumbler are not microwave safe but are hand wash recommended. Ceramic mugs like the 11 oz Aztec Mug are generally microwave and dishwasher safe. Always check product specs for care instructions."
    }
  ],
  "heroAltText": "Assorted custom drinkware including tumblers, mugs, and can coolers with printed logos on a white table.",
